<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_89_r1l19"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Erwelten vnd beſtetıgtem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l20"><expan>Ercʒbıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> ʒu Meincʒ etc <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l21"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> wır <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt
                                <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewd<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l22">daʒ eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vnd
                        erwırdıge <expan>p<ex>er</ex>ſone</expan> von
                            <expan>fürſehu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd gabe des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l23"><expan>allmechtıg<ex>en</ex></expan> gottes ʒu
                                <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> wırdıkeıt des
                                <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Stuls ʒu Meincʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l26"> erkorn <del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del>
                        gewelet <del rend="strikethrough">ſeyt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_89_line_1577026637817_4800">vnd beſtetıgt ıſt
                            </ab></add> Darcʒu wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürſtenlıch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l27">ſelıkeıt gelük vnd heyl wünſchen / Vnd
                                <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> demü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l28">tıklıch mıt <expan>g<ex>ancʒem</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>leiſſ</ex></expan> / Daʒ Jr vns vnd auch dıe
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l29"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet
                                <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> befolhen laſſen ſein günſtıge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l30"><expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> tun vnd
                                <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>amptleẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l31">tun befelhen / als <expan>ſelıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gedechtnuſſ / eẅr vorfarn vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r1l32">gnedıg <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>bıſh<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Vnd
                        vvır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<pb facs="#facs_90" id="44r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l2"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> auch wol getrawn / So ıſt vns von
                                <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l3">eın <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ Jr ein
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>Pfeıff<ex>er</ex>s</expan> begert / den wır be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l5">ſtellt <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / Den
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <del rend="strikethrough"> eren </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_90_r1l4">dıenſt </ab></add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darcʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_line_1577026680133_4835">geurlawbt vnd
                            <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mer ʒu eren
                            <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l6">da <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wır wıllıg ʒu
                                <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Denn wo wır
                            <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l8"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıenſt vnd
                                <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_89" id="43v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, erwelten und bestetigtem
                                <expan>erczbisch<ex>of</ex></expan> zu Meincz etc.,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewd<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>, daz ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> und erwirdige
                            <expan>p<ex>er</ex>sone</expan> von <expan>fürsehu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        und gabe des <expan>allmechtig<ex>en</ex></expan> gottes zu
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> wirdikeit des
                                <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> stuls zu Meincz erkorn, gewelet
                            <add>und bestetigt ist</add>, darczu wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> selikeit, gelük und heyl wünschen. Und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> demütiklich mit
                                <expan>g<ex>anczem</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>leiss</ex></expan>, daz ir uns und auch die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        befolhen lassen sein, günstige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> tun und
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>amptlewt<ex>en</ex></expan> und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> zu
                        tun befelhen als <expan>selig<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnuss ewr vorfarn,
                        unser gnedig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>bish<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<pb facs="#facs_90" id="44r"/>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> auch wol getrawn. So ist uns von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ein <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz ir ein <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>pfeiff<ex>er</ex>s</expan> begert, den wir bestellt
                                <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., den
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <add>dienst</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darczu geurlawbt. Und
                            <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mer zu eren
                            <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> tun, da <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wir
                        willig zu <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
